## Required Variables

### API Keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
# OR
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

### Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/dbname
# Get this from Vercel Postgres dashboard

### Frontend
VITE_API_URL=/api

## Optional Variables

### AI Model Selection
AI_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile
# For Groq: llama-3.3-70b-versatile
# For OpenAI: gpt-3.5-turbo or gpt-4

### Production Settings
NODE_ENV=production
PYTHON_VERSION=3.11
